0:32:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-agrees-bring-indian-migrant-workers-ease-job-crunch-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>独家：汇丰银行将改善与香港恒生银行的关系以降低风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-improve-ties-with-hong-kong-unit-hang-seng-mitigate-risk-say-sources-2024-02-16/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，由于担心中国经济逆风加剧和房地产业危机可能导致不良贷款增加，汇丰银行计划加强香港子公司恒生银行的风险管理。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 07:42:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-improve-ties-with-hong-kong-unit-hang-seng-mitigate-risk-say-sources-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国加强房地产行业“白名单”机制 - 媒体</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-steps-up-whitelist-mechanism-property-sector-media-2024-02-16/</link><description>据政府支持的媒体澎湃新闻报道，中国五家国有银行已在“白名单”机制下为超过8,200个住宅项目提供开发贷款，旨在为受危机打击的行业注入流动性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 06:46:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-steps-up-whitelist-mechanism-property-sector-media-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>红海危机帮助竞争对手夺取业务，印度小型出口商陷入困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-small-exporters-reel-red-sea-crisis-helps-rivals-nab-business-2024-02-16/</link><description>印度东部城市加尔各答的出口商 Atul Jhunjhunwala 正抓狂，由于红海危机增加了他的运输成本和时间，他刚刚失去了另一份订单。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 06:35:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-small-exporters-reel-red-sea-crisis-helps-rivals-nab-business-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>供应紧张之际，中国将在新加坡航展上展示国产客机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-show-off-homegrown-airliner-singapore-air-show-amid-supply-crunch-2024-02-16/</link><description>新加坡将于下周举办自新冠疫情边境限制结束以来首次举办亚洲最大的航空展，地区旅行将出现反弹，展会的军事方面将布满防御系统和紧张的武器买家。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 05:55:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-show-off-homegrown-airliner-singapore-air-show-amid-supply-crunch-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>香港当局在价值18亿美元的洗钱案中逮捕了七人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-authorities-arrest-seven-18-bln-money-laundering-case-2024-02-16/</link><description>香港当局周五表示，他们逮捕了 7 名涉嫌参与 18 亿美元洗钱案件的人，这是该金融中心有史以来规模最大的洗钱案件。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 05:29:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-authorities-arrest-seven-18-bln-money-laundering-case-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚葡萄酒制造商押注中国有望重新开放，并向香港大量发货</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/australian-wine-makers-bet-expected-china-reopening-with-big-shipments-hong-kong-2024-02-16/</link><description>根据行业数据和贸易数据，澳大利亚葡萄酒制造商已将数百万瓶葡萄酒运往香港，押注中国将很快取消对澳大利亚葡萄酒的关税并重振价值数亿美元的贸易。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 05:27:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/australian-wine-makers-bet-expected-china-reopening-with-big-shipments-hong-kong-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>股市摆脱了不完整的数据；黄金面临2024年最大单周跌幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-16/</link><description>周五全球股市连续第三天上涨，这得益于日本日经指数收于另一个 34 年高点的提振，以及随着数据恢复了 6 月份降息可能性而导致华尔街股市上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 02:12:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>生产者价格高于预期，美元上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-traders-weigh-economic-data-yen-fragile-2024-02-16/</link><description>数据显示全球最大经济体的生产者价格高于预期，证实了美联储将把降息周期开始时间推迟到年中的预期，周五美元上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 01:33:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-traders-weigh-economic-data-yen-fragile-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：利率希望胜过经济恐慌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-15/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 21:49:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>太平洋岛国对美国拖延资助感到担忧，对中国发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/anxious-about-us-funding-delay-pacific-island-nations-warn-about-china-2024-02-15/</link><description>美国战略盟友太平洋岛国的领导人对美国国会预算僵局越来越感到焦虑，这一僵局导致重要的新融资方案的批准被推迟，并警告说，中国正在积极寻求改变他们的忠诚度，包括对台湾的忠诚度。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 20:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/anxious-about-us-funding-delay-pacific-island-nations-warn-about-china-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车表示，巴西可持续发展规则不应让汽车变得更加昂贵</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brazil-sustainability-rules-should-not-make-cars-more-expensive-volkswagen-says-2024-02-15/</link><description>大众汽车巴西业务负责人西罗·波索博姆 (Ciro Possobom) 表示，巴西旨在促进该国汽车行业可持续发展投资的新激励计划需要避免使车辆变得更加昂贵。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 18:14:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brazil-sustainability-rules-should-not-make-cars-more-expensive-volkswagen-says-2024-02-15/</guid></item></channel></rss>